          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In macOS, the Display panel in System Preferences is used to set the default gamma for a display. Quartz also allows an application to provide its own custom gamma information, using functions such as ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/1456604-cgsetdisplaytransferbytable",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/1454126-cgsetdisplaytransferbyformula",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "These functions take ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CGGammaValue",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " arguments that specify:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A set of gamma table entries ranging from 0 to 1",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The positive real coefficients in a gamma equation",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
